data.meta_description:
Excited to start the new season with our First event, Focused Group Discussion( FGD) at Thiruvananthapuram, on My first steps with Cambridge. 
Kudos to our…
data.text: 🎉 Exciting News! 🎉 from #cambridge I am thrilled to share that our recent focused group discussion which was an incredible success, thanks to the outstanding efforts of our team and the enthusiastic participation of all attendees! 🚀 From start to finish, it was an unforgettable experience filled with knowledge sharing, networking, and camaraderie. The positive feedback we received has been overwhelming and deeply gratifying. 💬 I express my deep thanks to Sonali ma’am who conducted this session. I also want to express my heartfelt gratitude to Shweta Gangakhed , @vandana, @akansha, @karthikeyan who contributed to making this event a resounding success. Your dedication and support played a pivotal role in creating an atmosphere of inspiration and growth. 👏. My special thanks to Manish Doshi for all the support. As we continue to strive for excellence, events like these are a testament to the power of collaboration and the strength of our community. Together, we can achieve greatness and make a lasting impact in our industry. 🤝 If you missed this event, don't worry! Stay tuned for more exciting opportunities in the future, and let's keep the momentum going. Remember, success is a journey, and I am thrilled to have you all on this ride with us. 🚀 Here's to the next milestone together! 🎊 #cambridge #cambridgeuniversity Cambridge University Press & Assessment
